{"tid":322963,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣睇中文字都覺得佢地冇情緒","createTime":"2017-07-15T08:49:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-15T11:24:38.000Z","uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"800f6aa9fc301393427df1f9ae1721594fdf0cef","tid":322963,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T08:49:21.000Z","msg":"唔知點解睇中文字嗰啲字會覺得好機械<br />\n冇咩情緒，冇咩感情，呆呆滯滯，加晒感嘆號又好，加晒助語詞又好，都冇咩感覺<br />\n係廣東話先似係人講嘢，有情緒起伏，見字如見人<br />\n唔知係咪因為書面語嘅關係<br />\n因為依個情況係英文又唔覺，見到啲外國人打英文都覺得係有幽默感、有情緒、有恥笑，係唯獨對中文冇依個感覺<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇"},{"pid":"9fe5c13635cd3b4814e818407ec8853dcea1fff4","tid":322963,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T08:51:44.000Z","msg":"你打就真係冇乜情緒"},{"pid":"e1f42fc32c6a93d129d52d7a43f0626e589b9d2a","tid":322963,"uid":7430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T08:57:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你打就真係冇乜情緒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n反而覺得英文先無情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fd6471345adf63345a1e2f34b76a55cc2e5331c","tid":322963,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T11:24:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你打就真係冇乜情緒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n反而覺得英文先無情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n普通陳述都有情緒就死囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}